    {% filter markdown %}
    ## Behavior
    - The Title's width is 100% of its parent container. 
    - Text content will wrap when necessary. 
    - Content in the `metadata` slot will trail the heading if it wraps to another line. 

    ## Content
    - The Title's heading should be clear and concise. 
    - Set all text in sentence case. 
    - Use the `annotation`, `metadata`, and `subheading` affordances to provide additional context.
