{% block code_tab %}
  {% filter markdown %}
    ## Installation
    {% include "src/templates/partials/integration.njk" %}

    ## Attributes
    {% endfilter %}
    {% include "src/templates/partials/jsProps.njk" %}
    {% filter markdown %}
    | Attribute           | Type   | Validation                   | Default | Description                                                                                       |
    |---------------------|--------|------------------------------|---------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
    | `eds-border`        | string | `top`, `bottom`              | --      | If `top` or `bottom` is specified as a value, a border will be rendered above or below the Title. |

    ## Slots

    | Name         | Default content | Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
    | ------------ | --------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
    | `action`     | --              | Allows <eds-link eds-href="/components/button/button.html">Buttons</eds-link>, <eds-link eds-href="/components/link/link.html">Links</eds-link>, or other interactive elements to appear to the far right of the `heading` slot.      |
    | `annotation` | --              | Space reserved inline after the `metadata` slot. Typically used for a tooltip or other progressively revealed information about the Title.                                                                                            |
    | `heading`    | --              | Content that will render as the Title's heading.                                                                                                                                                                                      |
    | `metadata`   | --              | Text that appears inline after the `heading` slot.                                                                                                                                                                                    |
    | `subheading` | --              | Content that will appear below the `heading` slot.                                                                                                                                                                                    |

    ## Events
    The Title component does not emit any custom events.

    ## Methods
    The Title component does not implement any public methods.

    ## CSS helper classes
    CSS helper classes provide common styles needed for slotted content.

    | Class name               | Applies to                                      | Outcome                                                                     |
    | ------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
    | `.eds-title__annotation` | An element slotted within the `annotation` slot | Ensures proper alignment of the annotation.                                 |
    | `.eds-title__heading`    | An element slotted within the `heading` slot    | Ensures proper alignment of the heading and applies default heading styles. |
    | `.eds-title__metadata`   | An element slotted within the `metadata` slot   | Ensures proper alignment of the metadata.                                   |
    | `.eds-title__subheading` | An element slotted within the `subheading` slot | Ensures proper alignment of the subheading.                                 |


    ## CSS modifier classes
    {% include "src/templates/partials/cssModifiers.njk" %}

    | Class name                     | Applies to            | Outcome                                |
    | ------------------------------ | --------------------- | -------------------------------------  |
    | `.eds-title--border-bottom`    | `.eds-title-root`     | Adds a bottom border to the component. |
    | `.eds-title--border-top`       | `.eds-title-root`     | Adds a top border to the component.    |
    | `.eds-title__heading--level-1` | `.eds-title__heading` | Sets the "Level 1" heading style.      |
    | `.eds-title__heading--level-2` | `.eds-title__heading` | Sets the "Level 2" heading style.      |
    | `.eds-title__heading--level-3` | `.eds-title__heading` | Sets the "Level 3" heading style.      |
    | `.eds-title__heading--level-5` | `.eds-title__heading` | Sets the "Level 5" heading style.      |

  {% endfilter %}

